{"tid":2323921,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"愉XX(X健)用衣架襲擊街坊","createTime":"2020-12-13T14:04:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T04:53:12.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"efeb783b28b491897a4c79fc76506bb589f032c9","tid":2323921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:04:58.000Z","msg":"Shek William 石威廉<br />\n3 小時  &middot; <br />\n【注意繫穩戶外物件】<br />\n昨晚有街坊在愉健閣附近，被衣架擊中頭部流血，幸無大礙無需送院。北風逐漸增強，各位街坊記得繫穩戶外物品或取回室內，避免物件掉落擊傷途人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/131106099_2828323247443530_4100574925499741101_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=nxks-XFMUU4AX8TnL5i&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=5b093e3ebbe5e052c6cb242a42623d82&amp;oe=5FFAEFA0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F131106099_2828323247443530_4100574925499741101_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3Dnxks-XFMUU4AX8TnL5i%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3D5b093e3ebbe5e052c6cb242a42623d82%26oe%3D5FFAEFA0&h=546f8be8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8128600cc7ea5afe2ba1fd318769b4f31e31297","tid":2323921,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.takungpao.com/2019/1102/20191102042326714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.takungpao.com%2F2019%2F1102%2F20191102042326714.jpg&h=5ba26986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a2320bdc252a0e745dc56d8ca93ef3922f1093","tid":2323921,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T14:05:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/gZlOk6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FgZlOk6.gif&h=99b107da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1ffbabe612698321888d0